<item>
            <title>[LU-3245] FS root OBF regression</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3245</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Accessing the filesystem root by its FID fails with EINVAL. It seems that master and 2.3 are affected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;$ lfs path2fid /mnt/lustre&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x200000007:0x1:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
$ ls /mnt/lustre&lt;br/&gt;
$ ls /mnt/lustre/.lustre/fid/0x200000007:0x1:0x0&lt;br/&gt;
ls: cannot access /mnt/lustre/.lustre/fid/0x200000007:0x1:0x0: Invalid argument&lt;/p&gt;</description>
